text: Anikó Iglói (11 November 1908 - 12 April 2003) was a Hungarian alpine skier. She competed in two events at the 1948 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1908 births Category:2003 deaths Category:Hungarian female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Hungary Category:Alpine skiers at the 1948 Winter Olympics Category:People from Kremnica
